Class Controllers

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.Controllers
public final class Controllers extends Object
The list of keybinds for our controllers for the robot. Call ONE of these methods in RobotContainer's configureBindings() method.'

    • getControllerAxis

      public static double getControllerAxis(edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.button.CommandXboxController controller, Controllers.ControllerAxis controllerAxis, boolean scaled)
      Gets a given controller axis (a joystick value).
      Parameters:
      controller - The controller to get the axis from. Should probably pass a public field of Controllers
      controllerAxis - Enum representing which axis (left stick vs. right stick and x axis vs. y axis) to get.
      scaled - Whether or not to deadband and quadratically scale the axis.
      Returns:
      Axis value.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - If an enum value for ControllerAxis is passed that doesn't exist within that type

    • getControllerAxisSupplier

      public static Supplier<Double> getControllerAxisSupplier(edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.button.CommandXboxController controller, Controllers.ControllerAxis controllerAxis, boolean scaled)
      Gets supplier for a given controller axis (a joystick value).
      Parameters:
      controller - The controller to get the axis from. Should probably pass a public field of Controllers
      controllerAxis - Enum representing which axis (left stick vs. right stick and x axis vs. y axis) to get.
      scaled - Whether or not to deadband and quadratically scale the axis.
      Returns:
      Supplier that, when .get() is run, will return the requested axis value.
